          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0648P0-05489'>
        <a name='S5LV0648P0_20030604_GCR_73'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mrs-diana-maddock' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0648P0_20030604_GCR_73' title='Link to this speech by Mrs Diana Maddock' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mrs-diana-maddock" title="Mrs Diana Maddock">Baroness Maddock</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            I think that that precisely makes my point. If a regime has been in place that long, is it not time that we considered something else?
