            As I have no example to give of the kind of bodies that may involve, I offer that explanation on the basis that situations are always changing&#x2014;bodies merge and different bodies are created for different purposes&#x2014;and that we need flexibility. If I had any example of bodies to give, I suspect they would be listed in the Bill in any event.</p><p>
            In the draft regulation 22, examples are given of bodies, including the National Parks authorities, Broads Authority and the Lea Valley Regional Park Authority, which are not mainstream authorities. I hope that satisfies the noble Lord.
          </p>
