      </p>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0648P0-05607'>
        <a name='S5LV0648P0_20030604_GCR_191'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-peter-smith' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0648P0_20030604_GCR_191' title='Link to this speech by Mr Peter Smith' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
