            <q>Before Clause 25, insert the following new clause&#x2014;</q>
            <q>APPLICATION OF PROVISIONS OF THIS PART</q>
            <q>(1) The provisions of this Part shall be applied to those local authorities which have&#x2014;</q>
            <ol><li>(a) been assessed as weak in Corporate Performance Assessment overall;</li>
            <li>(b) been assessed as weak in Corporate Performance Assessment in "Use of Resources";</li>
